  },
  {
    "index": 1,
    "MessageID": 15226,
    "TextENGNew": "Shion Sonozaki's last confession is dubious.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 2,
    "MessageID": 15227,
    "TextENGNew": "Did the hag convince her that the Sonozaki family had nothing to do with it?",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 3,
    "MessageID": 15228,
    "TextENGNew": "Or is that the truth?",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 4,
    "MessageID": 15229,
    "TextENGNew": "In my own investigations so far, I've proven there are aspects of the curse which can't be explained by the Sonozaki family alone.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 5,
    "MessageID": 15230,
    "TextENGNew": "So, my notes were all bogus from the beginning.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 6,
    "MessageID": 15231,
    "TextENGNew": "These two hundred pages are full of bullshit.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 7,
    "MessageID": 15232,
    "TextENGNew": "I thought of burning this notebook.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 8,
    "MessageID": 15233,
    "TextENGNew": "But I won't do it.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 9,
    "MessageID": 15234,
    "TextENGNew": "This notebook proves my guilt.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 10,
    "MessageID": 15235,
    "TextENGNew": "I won't distort the facts.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 11,
    "MessageID": 15236,
    "TextENGNew": "I won't burn it.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 12,
    "MessageID": 15237,
    "TextENGNew": "After all, my life was only a notebook long.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 13,
    "MessageID": 15238,
    "TextENGNew": "I wonder if anybody will read this.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 14,
    "MessageID": 15239,
    "TextENGNew": "If somebody does, please let them learn something from my stupidity.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 15,
    "MessageID": 15240,
    "TextENGNew": "The series of mysterious deaths in Hinamizawa...",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 16,
    "MessageID": 15241,
    "TextENGNew": "Dubbed 'Oyashiro-sama's curse.'",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 17,
    "MessageID": 15242,
    "TextENGNew": "If you're reading this...",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 18,
    "MessageID": 15243,
    "TextENGNew": "...Please find the truth.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 19,
    "MessageID": 15244,
    "TextENGNew": "That's my only wish.",
    "significantChanges": false
  },
  {
    "index": 20,
    "MessageID": 15245,
    "TextENGNew": "June, 1983@k Mion Sonozaki",
    "significantChanges": false
  }
]
